data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO EARNEST MONEY NEVER BEING COLLECTED! This property features a custom-built home in a lakeside neighborhood. The neighborhood features an open green space for grilling and gathering. Possible boat or RV parking and Lake Views. Public Water Access is just a short drive down the road. The house is a perfect blend of relaxed and modern. Main level living is priority in the open plan with hardwood floors. Tons of windows allow for a flood of natural light and an open feel. The great room has high ceilings and a stone fireplace. Opening into a gourmet kitchen and Dining area. Perfect for entertaining. While the Primary Suite offers a well-appointed bath and dual closets. There is a second bedroom and full bath on the main floor, While the upper level has a 3rd bedroom, full bath and Huge Bonus Room.  The covered front porch and screen rear porch are perfect for enjoying the large yard while areas of the property have seasonal lake views. Come view this beautiful home Today!
